T02TD3718E:194a-4: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3718E:194a-5: dngos po'i de nyid rang bzhin 'od gsal mngon mdzad nas //
T02TD3718E:194a-6: gdul bya'i dbang gis sku yi cha byad sna tshogs dang //
T02TD3718E:194a-7: tshig dang yi ge dag gis de nyi de ston mdzad pa //
T02TD3718E:194a-8: rdo rje mi phyed gsum dngos sku la phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD3718E:194a-9: rab tu gsang ba blo mchog yul gyur gsang sngags don //
T02TD3718E:194a-10: log par rtogs pa'i dbang gis sgro 'dogs skur 'debs sheng //
T02TD3718E:194a-11: nyon mongs dbang gis sgra bzhin 'jug par byed pa rnams //
T02TD3718E:194a-12: go bar bya phyir mdor bsdus cung zhig bdag gis bris //
T02TD3718E:194a-13: bskal pa chen po rab mang bas //
T02TD3718E:194a-14: bgrod par bya ba'i sa rnams dang //
T02TD3718E:194a-15: 'og min la sogs zhing dag par //
T02TD3718E:194a-16: bsgom dang bzlas dang mchod stsogs kyis //
T02TD3718E:194a-19: rgyu dang rkyen ni gang dang gang //
T02TD3718E:194a-20: bya ba dang bcas byed pa gang //
T02TD3718E:194a-21: de yi grub pa gang zhig yin //
T02TD3718E:194a-22: grub pa de yis spyod pa gang //
T02TD3718E:194a-23: grub pa'i dus ni nges pa gang //
T02TD3718E:194a-25: bdag dang lha de'i bdag nyid gang//
T02TD3718E:194b-0: @194b sngags kyi de nyid ji lta bu //
T02TD3718E:194b-1: lam dang lam min gang dang gang //
T02TD3718E:194b-2: gzhi dang yan lag dam tshig dang //
T02TD3718E:194b-3: cho ga'i bya ba rnam nges gang //
T02TD3718E:194b-4: dper na skyes bu stobs chung ba'am //
T02TD3718E:194b-5: phyugs kyi shing rtas dus ring gis //
T02TD3718E:194b-6: bgrod par bya ba'i gnas der ni //
T02TD3718E:194b-7: rkang mgyogs grub pa'am nyi zlas ni //
T02TD3718E:194b-9: de bzhin pha rol phyin pa'am //
T02TD3718E:194b-10: lam gzhan dag la brten nas ni //
T02TD3718E:194b-11: yun rings 'jug par gyur pa deng //
T02TD3718E:194b-13: mnyam med mthu la brten phyir ro //
T02TD3718E:194b-14: de yang rgyu rkyen phun tshogs kyis //
T02TD3718E:194b-15: rgyu dang lus ngag yid kyi las //
T02TD3718E:194b-16: sngon tshe legs par spyad pa yis //
T02TD3718E:194b-17: da ltar rnam par smin pa'i rgyud //
T02TD3718E:194b-18: mtshan dang ldan pa'i lus thob cing //
T02TD3718E:194b-19: tshangs dbyangs ka la ping+ka'i ngag /'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug tshogs //
T02TD3718E:194b-20: nyon mongs bsrabs pa'i sems ldan pa'o //
T02TD3718E:194b-21: rkyen yang rnam pa gsum nyid de //
T02TD3718E:194b-22: 'jug dang sbyor dang sgrub pa yi //
T02TD3718E:194b-23: spyod pa rnam pa gsum nyid do //
T02TD3718E:194b-24: de la 'jug pa'i spyod pa ni //
T02TD3718E:194b-25: sngags la dad pa'i slob ma yis //
T02TD3718E:194b-26: bla ma yon tan ldan pa la //
T02TD3718E:194b-27: dus ring bsnyen pa sngon 'gro bas //
T02TD3718E:194b-28: mnyes nas gsol ba gdab byas la //
T02TD3718E:194b-30: rang gi 'dod lha gzung ba ste //
T02TD3718E:194b-31: de ni gzhi yi rkyen zhes bya //
T02TD3718E:194b-32: de la sbyor ba'i spyod pa ni //
T02TD3718E:194b-33: mthun pa'i gnas stsogs de dang der //
T02TD3718E:194b-34: dang por stong nyid byams stsogs dang //
T02TD3718E:194b-35: rang 'dod lha yi cho ga yis //
T02TD3718E:194b-36: thun gsum mam ni thun bzhi ru //
T02TD3718E:194b-37: bsgom dang bzlas dang kha don dang //
T02TD3718E:194b-38: gtor ma sbyin pa'am mchod stsogs brtson //
T02TD3718E:194b-39: sdig chen kun las grol nas ni //
T02TD3718E:194b-40: bskal pa du mar spyad pa yis //
T02TD3718E:194b-41: byang chub sems dpa' dang mtshungs 'gyur //
T02TD3718E:194b-43: gnyis pa yin par bstan pa yin //
T02TD3718E:194b-44: de la sgrub pa'i spyod pa ni //
T02TD3718E:194b-45: dper na legs par bkrus pa'i ras //
T02TD3718E:194b-46: kha dog rnams su bsgyur ba na //
T02TD3718E:194b-47: tshigs ni chung ste gzab 'os ltar //
T02TD3718E:194b-48: sgrub pa'i spyod pa'am bsgrims dgos kyi //
T02TD3718E:194b-49: ha cang dka' ba'ang ma yin no //
T02TD3718E:194b-50: sbyor ba'i spyod pas rgyud smin pa'i //
T02TD3718E:194b-51: gang zag bsgrub la 'jug pa ni //
T02TD3718E:194b-52: gnas dang grogs dang longs spyod dang //
T02TD3718E:194b-53: bsam pa ma yin pa rnams spangs //
T02TD3718E:195a-0: dmigs pa'i don la rtse gcig @195a * //
T02TD3718E:195a-1: gzhag /'di ni myur du 'phags pa'i rkyen //
T02TD3718E:195a-2: gsum pa yin par bstan pa yin //
T02TD3718E:195a-3: de la 'jug pa'i spyod pa ni //
T02TD3718E:195a-4: dngos grub skye ba zhing dang 'dra //
T02TD3718E:195a-5: de la sbyor ba'i spyod pa ni //
T02TD3718E:195a-7: de la sgrub pa'i spyod pa ni //
T02TD3718E:195a-8: 'bru yi tshogs rnams smin pa bzhin //
T02TD3718E:195a-9: de dag kun la'ang gtso bo ni //
T02TD3718E:195a-10: las bzang du mas smin byas pa'i //
T02TD3718E:195a-11: sems ni sa bon 'dra ba'i phyir //
T02TD3718E:195a-12: phul du byung ba'i rgyur rab gnas //
T02TD3718E:195a-13: de ltar rgyu rkyen phun tshogs pa'i //
T02TD3718E:195a-14: sngags pas sa rnams rab gnon cing //
T02TD3718E:195a-15: mngon par shes pa lngas rtse la //
T02TD3718E:195a-16: dag pa'i sangs rgyas zhing du 'gro / de la bya ba dang bcas pa'i //
T02TD3718E:195a-17: byed pa po dang 'dra bar ni //
T02TD3718E:195a-18: rnam pa gsum du shes bya ste //
T02TD3718E:195a-20: sems ni dmigs la rtse gcig dang //
T02TD3718E:195a-21: yang dag lta dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD3718E:195a-22: de lta'i bya ba dang ldan pa'i //
T02TD3718E:195a-23: grub pa'i dngos grub gang zhe na //
T02TD3718E:195a-24: lus dang gnas dang longs spyod dag / mi las khyad par 'phags pa ste //
T02TD3718E:195a-25: tshe la dbang bsgyur mi khom par //
T02TD3718E:195a-26: skye las gtan du grol ba dang //
T02TD3718E:195a-27: sangs rgyas 'byung dang phrad stsogs dang //
T02TD3718E:195a-28: 'dod yon lnga po shes bzhin du //
T02TD3718E:195a-30: bdag gzhan phan pa bskyed nus pa'o //
T02TD3718E:195a-31: grub pa'i spyod pa gang zhe na //
T02TD3718E:195a-32: yul dang dus ni de dang der //
T02TD3718E:195a-33: 'byor pa'i bde ba la spyod cing //
T02TD3718E:195a-34: de bzhin 'phags pa rnams la yang //
T02TD3718E:195a-35: ci nus par ni mchod pa dang //
T02TD3718E:195a-36: phan gdags tshar gcod kyis 'dul ba'i //
T02TD3718E:195a-37: sems can rnams la rjes mthun par //
T02TD3718E:195a-39: dmyal la sogs par yud tsam la'ang //
T02TD3718E:195a-40: bsil dang drod sogs sbyin pa dang //
T02TD3718E:195a-41: de bzhin sems can sna chogs la //
T02TD3718E:195a-42: chos rnams sna tshogs ston pa ste //
T02TD3718E:195a-43: sman gyi ljon shing chen po ltar //
T02TD3718E:195a-44: mthong dang thos dang reg pa dang //
T02TD3718E:195a-45: dran pas kun la phan gyur pa'o //
T02TD3718E:195a-46: grub pa'i dus ni gang zhe na //
T02TD3718E:195a-47: rgyu dang rkyen ne phun tshogs shing //
T02TD3718E:195a-48: rgyun du bzlas dang bsgom pa dang //
T02TD3718E:195a-49: rgyal ba sras bcas la dad pa'i //
T02TD3718E:195a-50: dka' thub can gyis dngos grub ni //
T02TD3718E:195a-52: rgyu dang ldan yang rkyen 'ga' zhig / ma chang ba ni tshe gsum gyis //
T02TD3718E:195a-53: stong nyid legs mthong dus med grol//
T02TD3718E:195b-0: @195b 'bras bu dman pa rnam mang las //
T02TD3718E:195b-1: nyan thos rang rgyal 'grub pa ni //
T02TD3718E:195b-2: tsandan shing ni bsil mod kyang //
T02TD3718E:195b-3: byug pa'i sbyor bas ma bsten par //
T02TD3718E:195b-4: bung shing sbyor bas bsten na ni //
T02TD3718E:195b-5: shin tu sreg cing gdung par 'gyur //
T02TD3718E:195b-6: de bzhin gsang sngags sgor spyod pas //
T02TD3718E:195b-7: sems can kun gyi nyon mongs pa'i//
T02TD3718E:195b-8: gdung pa zhi byed yin na yang //
T02TD3718E:195b-9: snying rje'i lcags kyu dang bral zhing //
T02TD3718E:195b-10: mtshan med dgon par zhugs gyur na //
T02TD3718E:195b-11: theg pa dman pas mya ngan 'da' //
T02TD3718E:195b-12: des na 'bras bu dman zhes bya //
T02TD3718E:195b-13: bdag lus sha khrag rus pa dang //
T02TD3718E:195b-14: rtsa rgyus spu sogs 'dus pa tsam //
T02TD3718E:195b-15: bdag tu brjod par bya ba yin //
T02TD3718E:195b-16: chos dbyings sbyor ba'i gsang sngags dang //
T02TD3718E:195b-17: de nyid la ni mos pa'i mthus //
T02TD3718E:195b-18: lha yis gzugs su 'byung ba'i rten //
T02TD3718E:195b-19: khyad par can du gnas pa ni //
T02TD3718E:195b-20: rags pa'i bdag gi de nyid yin //
T02TD3718E:195b-21: gzhan yang rtog pa zhib pa dag /'khor bar mngon par phyogs pa'i sems //
T02TD3718E:195b-22: lus dang gnas dang longs spyod dang //
T02TD3718E:195b-23: dba' rlabs ldan pa 'di kho na //
T02TD3718E:195b-24: bdag tu brjod pa bzhi ru 'dod //
T02TD3718E:195b-25: de ni gzung 'dzin dang bral zhing //
T02TD3718E:195b-26: rang rig 'od gsal dngos gyur pa //
T02TD3718E:195b-27: bdag gi de nyid ces brjod do //
T02TD3718E:195b-28: de la lha yi de nyid ni //
T02TD3718E:195b-29: rang sngags tshes dbyings thugs chud cing //
T02TD3718E:195b-30: nam mkha'i ngos ltar gur pa las //
T02TD3718E:195b-31: klu rnams kyi ni byin rlabs kyis //
T02TD3718E:195b-32: mdog dang dbyibs ni tha dad pa'i //
T02TD3718E:195b-33: sprin rnams nam mkhar 'byung ba ltar //
T02TD3718E:195b-34: lha yi sku ru 'byung ba yin //
T02TD3718E:195b-35: rnam thar sgo gsum gyis brtags pas //
T02TD3718E:195b-37: de la sngags kyi de nyid ni //
T02TD3718E:195b-38: thabs dang shes rab chul gnas lha //
T02TD3718E:195b-39: mi rtog bzhin du der ston cing //
T02TD3718E:195b-40: spyan drangs mchod nas gshegs gsol pa'o //
T02TD3718E:195b-41: lam ni spyod pa rnam gsum sogs //
T02TD3718E:195b-42: ji skad gong du sngar bstan pa'o //
T02TD3718E:195b-43: lam ma yin pa 'di lta ste //
T02TD3718E:195b-44: log par 'jug cing tshol ba ste //
T02TD3718E:195b-45: bkag pa'i mi dge bcu spyod pa'o //
T02TD3718E:195b-46: dpar na mu stegs can 'ga' zhig /'jug pa'i spyod pa'i dus na yang //
T02TD3718E:195b-47: bud med bsten pa'i dbang bskur bzhin //
T02TD3718E:195b-48: thog ma me nas der zhen pas //
T02TD3718E:195b-49: sbyor ba'i spyod pa'i dus na yang //
T02TD3718E:195b-50: de la 'khyud cing zhen pa yis //
T02TD3718E:195b-51: bsgom dang bzlas sogs byed na yang //
T02TD3718E:196a-2: sgrub pa'i spyod pa'i dus na yang //
T02TD3718E:196a-3: de yi tha snyad la dga' zhing //
T02TD3718E:196a-4: tshul bzhin ma yin yid byed pas //
T02TD3718E:196a-6: rmad byung thob par ga la 'gyur //
T02TD3718E:196a-7: de bzhin zhe sdang gti mug sogs //
T02TD3718E:196a-8: sngon du song bas byas pa'i las //
T02TD3718E:196a-9: srog gcod ma byin len pa dang //
T02TD3718E:196a-10: brdzun du smra dang phra ma sogs //
T02TD3718E:196a-11: de dag thams cad lam min bstan //
T02TD3718E:196a-12: de la gzhi yi dam tshig ni //
T02TD3718E:196a-13: rnam pa bzhir ni shes bya ste //
T02TD3718E:196a-14: yang dag lta dang ldan pa dang //
T02TD3718E:196a-15: dkon mchog gsum po mi spong dang //
T02TD3718E:196a-16: byang chub sems dang ldan pa dang //
T02TD3718E:196a-17: dbang bskur yang dag mi spong ba'o //
T02TD3718E:196a-18: de la yan lag dam tshig ni //
T02TD3718E:196a-19: bzhi po de la brten pa yis //
T02TD3718E:196a-20: thun mong thun mong ma yin pa'i //
T02TD3718E:196a-21: bye brag lhag pa thams cad do //
T02TD3718E:196a-22: cho ga'i bya ba rnam nges ni //
T02TD3718E:196a-23: yang dag lta sogs gsum ldan zhing //
T02TD3718E:196a-24: bla ma mnyes byed bslab la gus //
T02TD3718E:196a-25: dus gsum lha mchod klog 'don zlos //
T02TD3718E:196a-26: rnam thar sgo gsum la gzhol zhing //
T02TD3718E:196a-27: dmigs pa gcig la brtan par bya //
T02TD3718E:196a-28: byang chub sems dpa' rab byung bas //
T02TD3718E:196a-29: rang gi 'dul dang cho ga las //
T02TD3718E:196a-31: sngags kyi dngos grub la reg bya //
T02TD3718E:196a-32: khyim par gyur pa'i sngags pa yis //
T02TD3718E:196a-33: rab tu byung ba'i sngags pa dag / bdag gi slob mar gyur pa na //
T02TD3718E:196a-34: rkang pa bkru dang phyag la sogs //
T02TD3718E:196a-35: nam yang bdag gir mi bya'o //
T02TD3718E:196a-36: rtag tu rab tu byung ba la //
T02TD3718E:196a-38: gus pas bsnyen bkur bya ba yin //
T02TD3718E:196a-39: sangs rgyas bstan pa rin chen sgron //
T02TD3718E:196a-40: 'bar ba'i snod ni dka' thub can //
T02TD3718E:196a-42: dge slong rnams ni yin phyir ro //
T02TD3718E:196a-43: de ltar dgongs pa can gyi gsung //
T02TD3718E:196a-44: dgongs bcas dgongs min ji lta bar //
T02TD3718E:196a-45: mdor bsdus bdag gis bris pa las //
T02TD3718E:196a-46: ston ka'i zla ba ltar dkar ba'i //
T02TD3718E:196a-47: dge ba cung zhig gang thob des //
T02TD3718E:196a-48: 'gro bas ma nor lam rtogs shog / ma nor rgyud kyi don brten nas //
T02TD3718E:196a-49: blo chung rnams phyir bris pa la //
T02TD3718E:196a-50: tshig dang don la 'khrul pa dag / mkhas pa rnams kyis bzod par mdzod //
T02TD3718E:196b-0: gsang sngags la 'jug pa'i rab tu @196b byed pa drug cu pa slob dpon dzny'a na a'a ka ras mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3718E:196b-2: // / panti ta dzny'a na a'a ka ra nyid dang /
T02TD3718E:196b-3: lo ts'a ba dge slong tshul khrims rgyal bas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
